{"tid":1695641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［朝早抗爭］返工日子18區開花 香港人可唔可以早起身一次","createTime":"2019-11-05T17:55:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T11:08:42.000Z","uid":76038,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ff4dc624558d731ffa78622ec12c60f1c9f919a0","tid":1695641,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:55:25.000Z","msg":"要突破樽頸 比到壓力政府 <br />\n就要令到香港人被罷工 癱瘓香港運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家一次港島/九龍大遊行拉幾多手足 大家都知<br />\n就算平日夜晚各區開花 到第二朝香港人都係如常返工返學  朝早同夜晚根本兩個世界黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每一區召集到500個以上手足已經做到好多野<br />\n塞路塞鐵，黨鐵封站，到時被罷工既同路人自然會黎幫拖，比哂藉口佢地唔返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間最好就6:30-7:00就係各區集合到足夠人數 ，可以係各區tg group投票先，到時真係會出黎既手足先好投<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人可唔可以早起身一次，返少幾日工？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f68af9d157d0805decde3dc8b77db13e3e97ac","tid":1695641,"uid":312526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:56:06.000Z","msg":"聽日？"},{"pid":"4f6928633790c0bc0ff3e252b302e0a7dbaff267","tid":1695641,"uid":312526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:56:26.000Z","msg":"集中一個地方先拉"},{"pid":"025ab9023fcd113e489226e08fadad837af30562","tid":1695641,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f6928633790c0bc0ff3e252b302e0a7dbaff267","tid":1695641,"uid":312526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:56:26.000Z","msg":"集中一個地方先拉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:59:07.000Z","msg":"集中一個地方做唔到癱瘓全港既效果 <br />\n同埋時間太早 最好係自己果區"},{"pid":"800bc4d338c7610868b068f44ea58cf9820dba30","tid":1695641,"uid":312526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"025ab9023fcd113e489226e08fadad837af30562","tid":1695641,"uid":76038,"like":0